{"id": 1068, "genre": 1001, "title": "你经历过哪些无法忍受的团队建设？", "description": "要么幼稚要么无聊，要么既幼稚又无聊，老板们还能想出点新招吗？（题图来自：Sam Chivers）", "record_count": 3636, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183610YqScXFnpmyw36QNo.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-05T03:53:46Z", "options": [{"id": 95513, "content": "饭桌上的套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663454}, {"id": 95518, "content": "每次聚会都是吃饭，唱歌，意义在哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668232}, {"id": 95557, "content": "一言不合就做游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343510}, {"id": 95497, "content": "同学聚会什么的其实有点尴尬啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659826}, {"id": 95488, "content": "每天工作心里面！督促销售顾问的工作让我22岁的年龄不错了50岁的大妈！天天啰里八嗦的自己都够累了还不领情", "image": "img/option/option/20160705150952MblIfCQ0B7nzx3jv.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668037}, {"id": 95489, "content": "打着团队的幌子，结果让一个人去完成", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659936}, {"id": 95494, "content": "组织去九华山爬山拜佛，不去的要交200块钱，理由是不积极参与团队建设，我说大姨妈来了不舒服，老板说那从下个月工资里扣，对，就是洪涝成灾的上周末。（手动微笑脸）", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592443}, {"id": 95504, "content": "努力把工作做好不是为了我们而是为你们自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668103}, {"id": 95514, "content": "家文化，一言不合立刻罚款，乐捐，带猪脸面具。家文化，别闹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668205}, {"id": 91172, "content": "做户外拓展，像教小朋友一样教给大家要团结什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 572, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 91173, "content": "过节大家一起包粽子，包饺子，然后积攒一堆活加班补上", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95525, "content": "唱K", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 13689}, {"id": 95531, "content": "和气生财，我们的气要聚在一起才能生财……生你妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433623}, {"id": 95535, "content": "开早会！说什么感谢公司，还期待?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668363}, {"id": 95543, "content": "学校是我家，爱护靠大家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651388}, {"id": 95545, "content": "学生组织每周例会，真的到最后都不知道开会的意义在哪里了，除了混脸熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159633}, {"id": 95560, "content": "没有预算，没钱，请不起人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668528}, {"id": 95491, "content": "还斤斤计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566983}, {"id": 95492, "content": "所有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 101893, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672711}, {"id": 96263, "content": "嘿嘿我最强，嘿嘿我最棒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601788}, {"id": 95496, "content": "除了吃喝就是吃喝，猪都出圈了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668059}, {"id": 95498, "content": "游戏两小时，讲话一小时，吃饭一小时，总之把时间安排的满满的", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579627}, {"id": 95501, "content": "我要幸福", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668091}, {"id": 95502, "content": "我要幸福\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668091}, {"id": 95507, "content": "只要在工作日团建，就好了，干什么都行。", "image": "img/option/option/20160705161805fDNw6csdZ24b1BEP.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668108}, {"id": 95510, "content": "中层为了让大领导满意，指使我们天天忙到凌晨，先忙团建，工作都要抽空或加班处理。最后团建开始，我躲在房间里累哭。还好那个公司年年亏损20多个亿", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160746}, {"id": 95515, "content": "Teambuilding活动，领导只希望员工积极表演表现，可问题是大家就只想好好玩耍而不是被逼着去排练节目啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668218}, {"id": 95516, "content": "杜兰特加盟勇士", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159718}, {"id": 95520, "content": "让同事之间互相斗，就像皇帝看儿子们斗一样，表面上是促发大家的狼性，其实对团队一点也不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524217}, {"id": 91171, "content": "年会领导讲话半天，表演节目半天，过了12点才抽奖", "image": null, "praise_count": 245, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 91174, "content": "生日会除了吃东西还要做游戏，尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 307, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95527, "content": "用画饼的形式告诉我们公司未来的发展，承诺的事情，永远都是折半", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668299}, {"id": 91176, "content": "老板开例会讲公司未来规划，一个人讲了一个下午，我睡了两觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 95528, "content": "一年一次团建", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116212}, {"id": 95529, "content": "吃吃，喝喝，玩玩儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668310}, {"id": 95530, "content": "公司活动，动不动删这删那（经费不足），删完还说：没有效果。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375176}, {"id": 95532, "content": "米撒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668346}, {"id": 95533, "content": "大学时每月一次的团组织生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72816}, {"id": 95534, "content": "整天中午做游戏，说是活跃气氛，每天喊口号", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668351}, {"id": 96047, "content": "想到一出是一出，朝令夕改。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670713}, {"id": 95536, "content": "我们是一家人。我们是一个团队。我们要多相互沟通。我们是平等的。。。。我呸。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668371}, {"id": 95537, "content": "拍视频歌颂vp", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668403}, {"id": 95538, "content": "年会！表演节目，简直惨无人道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430767}, {"id": 95539, "content": "真人CS", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 6382}, {"id": 95540, "content": "说的民主民主，其实永远都是她自己一锤定音", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 387354}, {"id": 100148, "content": "加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686180}, {"id": 95541, "content": "看到一个团队发展好，就拆了重新在组建", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668415}, {"id": 95542, "content": "玩什么过电网，哭的结束了都没喘过气，擦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517620}, {"id": 95544, "content": "基本观众", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159633}]}